{"tid":210497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「懺悔咗嘅壞人」翁靜晶唔信賊王洗心革面","createTime":"2017-04-21T03:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T03:51:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4805b23e4af22f43f2457d947397b03be2da7a13","tid":210497,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19997052&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19997052%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNngKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=90dd1208\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19997052%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170421&h=cd181e29\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19997052&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170421</a><br />\n<br />\n「懺悔咗嘅壞人」<br />\n翁靜晶唔信賊王洗心革面<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n賊王葉繼歡日前因癌病逝世，終年55歲。一直協助葉繼歡的街工梁耀忠出席電台節目時指，葉繼歡早前就懲教署拒絕給予中醫治療提請司法覆核，已獲法庭批出許可，但葉未等及已離世，他直言「覺得幾可惜」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指其親屬可提出由於葉繼歡沒有接受中醫治療而離世，作為繼續進行司法覆核程序的理由，否則法庭會終止程序。<br />\n<br />\n梁耀忠指，葉繼歡關注在囚人士權益，如爭取可使用保溫杯，又會向他反映囚友遇到的問題，希望他幫忙，形容葉繼歡相當關心別人。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【即時文摘】葉繼歡與兩男子微妙關係（李碧華）<br />\n<br />\n即時果籽&nbsp;11小時前"}]}